Rating: 2
I thought the cakes were good but not great. The expresso/cinammon spice did add a lot of wonderful flavor. However, I found it a bit difficult to unmold the "not-quite-done" cakes from the fluted tart pans. And I felt the cakes would have tasted better if cooked about 4-5 minutes longer.

